    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadzone Haunt</strong> is a wave-based First-Person Zombie Shooter. Customize your loadout, upgrade weapons, and use perks &amp; power-ups to dominate the demons. Experience smooth movement, satisfying gunplay, and a new approach to weapon camo customization. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229040/extras/dadca50d0573cbb590dd8407c01b6caa.poster.avif?t=1752114446\" width=608 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229040/extras/dadca50d0573cbb590dd8407c01b6caa.webm?t=1752114446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229040/extras/dadca50d0573cbb590dd8407c01b6caa.mp4?t=1752114446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >6 Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadzone Haunt</strong> offers six exciting game modes to keep gameplay fresh and challenging. Survive endless waves in <strong>Classic</strong>, push your limits in the intense <strong>10 Rounds</strong> mode, or face the tension of <strong>Battle Royale</strong>, where a shrinking gas zone keeps the pressure high. <strong>Perked Up</strong> starts you off with all perks unlocked. For different challenges, try the <strong>Easy</strong> or <strong>Extreme</strong> modes designed to suit varying skill levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >7 Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through <strong>seven uniquely designed maps</strong>, each with its own atmosphere and tactical opportunities. Battle zombies in the <strong>Bowling Alley</strong>, cross the rain-soaked <strong>Bridge</strong>, explore the <strong>Art Gallery</strong>, or survive the snowy <strong>Winter Village</strong>. Take on the abandoned <strong>Private Golf Villa</strong>, fight your way through the <strong>Prison</strong>, or defend the <strong>Airbase Hangar</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >11 Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 11 different weapons including <strong>shotguns</strong>, <strong>assault rifles</strong>, <strong>SMGs</strong>, <strong>pistols</strong>, <strong>full-auto pistols</strong>, and <strong>melee weapons</strong> to fit your playstyle. <strong>Upgrade</strong> them and blast through the zombie hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >10 Perks &amp; 4 Power-Ups</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your strategy with <strong>10 unique perks</strong> like <strong>faster reload</strong>, <strong>increased fire rate</strong>, and <strong>extra health</strong>, plus 4 powerful power-ups to help you <strong>survive the fight</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >10.5 Million Camo Variations (Camo Mixing)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Setting a <strong>new standard in FPS games</strong>, the <strong>Camo Mixing Tool</strong> lets you <strong>combine three different</strong> camos and <strong>fully customize the pattern and brightness</strong>. This opens up <strong>over 10 million unique combinations</strong> to make your weapons <strong>truly your own</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamepad Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadzone Haunt supports both <strong>controllers</strong> and <strong>mouse &amp; keyboard</strong>, delivering a <strong>true FPS experience</strong> on <strong>controller</strong> with <strong>customizable deadzones</strong>, <strong>optional aim assist</strong>, <strong>optimized aim response curves</strong> for smooth control, separate <strong>sensitivity settings</strong> for regular and ADS aiming, plus <strong>full button remapping</strong> to tailor controls to your preference.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Made by a gamer, for gamers.</strong></h2>",
